  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1080">
<l>eṟṟiṟ kuriyar kayavaroṉ ṟuṟṟakkāl</l>
<l>viṟṟaṟ kuriyar viraintu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The base will hasten to sell themselves as soon as a calamity has befallen them. For what else are they fitted ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
